2056</FONT></TD></TR>\n<TR STYLE=\"vertical-align: top\">\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt none; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: normal 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif\">Dial in:</FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt none; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: normal 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif\">647 427 7450</FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt none; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: normal 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif\">Pass code:</FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt none; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: normal 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif\">930 298 43</FONT></TD></TR>\n<TR STYLE=\"vertical-align: top\">\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt none; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: normal 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif\">Toll free:</FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt none; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: normal 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif\">1 888 231 8191</FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt none; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic\">&nbsp;</TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt none; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic\">&nbsp;</TD></TR>\n</TABLE>\n\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: italic 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal\">&nbsp;</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: italic 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal\">&nbsp;</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0 0 6pt\"><B>About Eldorado Gold</B></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\">Eldorado is a leading mid-tier gold producer\nwith mining, development and exploration operations in Turkey, Greece, Romania, Serbia, Brazil and Canada. The Company&rsquo;s\nsuccess to date is based on a highly skilled workforce, safe and responsible operations, a portfolio of high-quality assets, and\nlong-term partnerships with the communities where we operate. Eldorado&rsquo;s common shares trade on the Toronto Stock Exchange\n(TSX: ELD) and the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE: EGO).</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 8pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0 0 6pt\"><I>&nbsp;</I></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0 0 6pt; text-align: justify\"><B>Contact</B></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\">Krista Muhr, Vice President Investor Relations\n&amp; Corporate Communications</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\">Eldorado Gold Corporation</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\">604 687 4018 or 1 888 353 8166</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\">kristam@eldoradogold.com</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\">www.eldoradogold.com</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: bold 14pt Calibri, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0; text-align: center\"></P>\n\n<!-- Field: Page; Sequence: 1 -->\n    <DIV STYLE=\"margin-bottom: 6pt\"><TABLE CELLP